Read the COPYING file to understand your rights.
This is a package of Polish News Module theme for Superkaramba. 
It was tested with versions 0.29 from rpm and source.
The 0.29 version of SuperKaramba is REQUIRED by "Polish News Module 4.10" to work
Additionally xwininfo, kdialog and kfmclient programs are also required.
*********************************************************************************

Please read the INSTALL file to understand how to install the theme.
To prepare this theme for work don't forget to change permisions and ownership 
on the whole catalog to YOUR favourite user. ;)
Without that our theme wouldn't work at all.

*********************************************************************************
To use news links in the panel with your favourite browser, change the "kfmclient" setting in your KDE environment.

Please read CHANGELOG to find out how the theme was developed. 
We might have here some bugs yet, so...  don't hasitate to inform us ;-)

Good luck and have fun.
maciunio & lookanio
